node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Vin Diesel on June 06, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: Weeks away from the F9 release... in preproduction for the finale that starts only months from now... @meadowwalker sends me this image and tells me how happy the photo makes her feel. Naturally, one gets filled with emotion, purpose and ultimately gratitude. Eternal brotherhood is a blessing beyond words. Hope to make you proud... All love, Always.
